# Disk Monitoring using DUF - Disk Usage/Free Utility (Linux, BSD, macOS & Windows)

** df tool is vanila flavour 
** dfu is more organized and presentable

Features :

- overview of all mounted devices
- Themes
- List of inodes
- export in JSON
- sort options

Find more on:  https://github.com/muesli/duf

# Install in ubuntu distro

$ wget https://github.com/muesli/duf/releases/download/v0.8.1/duf_0.8.1_linux_amd64.deb

$ sudo dpkg -i duf_0.8.1_linux_amd64.deb 

$ duf 
